"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Individuals become a byword</h2>\n<h3>As a punishment for idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:7-Ezek14:8\">EZK 14:7–14:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>As a trial of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:6\">JOB 17:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:9\">JOB 30:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's people become a byword</h2>\n<h3>As a punishment for disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:37\">DEU 28:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:6-1Kgs9:9\">1KI 9:6–9:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:19-2Chr7:22\">2CH 7:19–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:8-Jer24:10\">JER 24:8–24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:1-Ezek23:10\">EZK 23:1–23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:17\">JOL 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>As a trial of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:9-Ps44:26\">PSA 44:9–44:26</a></strong></p>",
